Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.69,0:00:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A world... Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.29,0:00:14.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A world for you who seek freedom
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.13,0:00:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,stretches out right before your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.30,0:00:21.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If your endless dreams are your guide,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.30,0:00:25.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,surpass them, under the flag of your beliefs!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.48,0:00:35.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Making a splash,\NI've just started on my search
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.98,0:00:40.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heading towards a world without end
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.49,0:00:45.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My heart bursting with enthusiasm,\NI'll go to the ends of the earth
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.66,0:00:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In search of light yet unseen
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.00,0:01:04.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When the summer sun\Nsways the sails of my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.11,0:01:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the cue to open the door to a new world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.62,0:01:18.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sailing through the rocky waves of despair
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.62,0:01:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We head beyond the horizon
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.30,0:01:31.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Making a splash,\NI've just started on my search
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.97,0:01:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heading towards a world without end
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.47,0:01:41.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My heart bursting with enthusiasm,\NI'll go to the ends of the earth
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.65,0:01:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In search of light yet unseen
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.66,0:02:00.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"And So, the Legend Begins!\NTo the Other Side of the Rainbow"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.61,0:02:19.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father, it's an even bigger\Nharvest than we anticipated.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.28,0:02:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take it! Take every last bit of treasure in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.63,0:02:29.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Charge!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.96,0:02:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Guys!\N--Don't do anything crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.30,0:02:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the Pumpkin Pirates' territory!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.97,0:02:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until Rapa Nui gets back,\Nit's up to us to defend it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.30,0:02:39.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Professor!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.64,0:02:43.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm one of the Pumpkin Pirates, too!\NI'll fight alongside you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.98,0:02:46.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll help you out, Pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.31,0:02:50.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Professor!\N--They got me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.99,0:02:57.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How come you guys are having\Ntrouble against those kids?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.32,0:02:59.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wetton...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.99,0:03:02.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's still his same, young self!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.26,0:03:06.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you see, I'm Grandpa\NWetton's grandson, Lake.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.26,0:03:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Do I really look like him?\N--Yeah, a dead ringer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.60,0:03:13.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am, huh? My grandpa was\Nas handsome as I am, was he?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.27,0:03:14.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.94,0:03:16.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a weirdo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.61,0:03:19.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys hand over your\Ntreasure, nice and easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.28,0:03:22.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you refuse, I'll burn you to a\Ncrisp with this electroshock suit!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.28,0:03:24.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out! He uses electricity!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.62,0:03:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heh! Electricity, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.29,0:03:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And here I was just itching\Nto wreak a little havoc, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.96,0:03:35.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take your electricity, and cut\Nit clean in half with my sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.96,0:03:38.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, electricity doesn't work that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.96,0:03:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This will be interesting. Just try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.30,0:03:44.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was hoping you'd say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.64,0:03:54.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's quiet, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.48,0:03:56.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.65,0:03:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think everyone's all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.98,0:04:02.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Who knows?\N-- "Who knows?"  You can't say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.25,0:04:04.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you concerned about everyone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.59,0:04:07.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They don't need our concern.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.26,0:04:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Instead, I'm concerned about that\Ndamn mayor coming back alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.60,0:04:12.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.93,0:04:15.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Luffy and the others take\Ncare of that damn mayor,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.93,0:04:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then I won't be able to get him back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.60,0:04:20.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. I guess there is that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.94,0:04:24.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Coming?\N--Yeah. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.61,0:04:31.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum... Rocket!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.95,0:04:33.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.29,0:04:41.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoo, we stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.29,0:04:43.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.96,0:04:48.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You've got some nerve,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.63,0:04:51.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,coming into the Rainbow Mist\Nwithout my permission!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.64,0:04:54.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to pay the 50 million-Berry\N"entering on your own" tax!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.64,0:04:56.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--No way.\N--What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.27,0:04:59.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying you won't\Nfollow Wetton-sama's orders?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.64,0:05:01.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wetton? That's you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.58,0:05:06.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. I am the grand, puffed-up\Nmayor of all of Luluka, Wetton!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.58,0:05:09.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? You, who were once\Na pirate, are now the mayor?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.92,0:05:11.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What, is that so wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.59,0:05:15.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Captain! That's him!\NHe's the one who stole our ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.26,0:05:16.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.93,0:05:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're that kid from back then?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.60,0:05:25.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You, the one who burned down\Nthe town, are now the mayor?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.94,0:05:28.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't accept it! No way do I accept this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.61,0:05:30.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You shut your mouth!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.61,0:05:32.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rapa Nui!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.61,0:05:37.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kid, being the mayor is nice.\NI'm able to stay at my desk,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.95,0:05:42.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and rake in the money I swindle\Nfrom all the foolish citizens.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.29,0:05:44.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have to wander the\Nseas in search of my prey,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.62,0:05:48.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or get hunted down by the navy!\NEvery day is a carefree paradise.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.96,0:05:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no other trade as easy as this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.30,0:05:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once you are reborn, you too\Nwill obtain power, as I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.30,0:06:00.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no use going on being a petty pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.24,0:06:04.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.24,0:06:08.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Captain!\N--Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.92,0:06:17.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you...! What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.26,0:06:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know what a real pirate is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.93,0:06:23.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.93,0:06:25.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.93,0:06:31.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't need power.\NWe pirates have a dream, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.94,0:06:34.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-A dream, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.61,0:06:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My electroshock suit is invincible!\NYou cannot escape from it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.28,0:06:46.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Escape? Who, me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.28,0:06:49.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, I'm gonna cut that\Nelectricity of yours in half!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.95,0:06:53.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said, where's the sense\Nin trying to cut electricity?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.62,0:06:55.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall I cut it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.63,0:06:58.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this! Rolling Thunder!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.57,0:07:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What's going on here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.90,0:07:05.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That suit he's so proud of\Ndoesn't seem to be of much use
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.24,0:07:07.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,once the plug is pulled.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.91,0:07:11.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! How can this happen?!\NPut it back! Put it back, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.58,0:07:14.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You jackass! That's no fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.91,0:07:18.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help me! I'm sinking! I'm sinking!\NAh, I can't open the top!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.92,0:07:20.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me cut something...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.92,0:07:28.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A dream, you say? What is it? Tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.93,0:07:31.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone knows what your dream is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.93,0:07:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just want to obtain\Nriches of gold and silver.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.60,0:07:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That will come falling into your lap\Non its own, if you have power.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.60,0:07:45.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A pirate's dream is to be\Nthe greatest man on the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.95,0:07:51.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the man who will be king of the pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.62,0:07:53.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.95,0:07:55.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.62,0:08:02.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one has ever defied me and lived!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.23,0:08:04.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll blow you away, right down to your bones!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.56,0:08:07.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Wait, Captain!\N--Father, what about me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.57,0:08:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do I care?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.90,0:08:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.58,0:08:21.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that? What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.92,0:08:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rainbow Tower...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.25,0:08:32.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's collapsing...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.60,0:08:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it, what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.60,0:08:47.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's abandoned us!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.27,0:08:53.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wetton, you bastard! You're not\Nthe captain anymore, dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.95,0:08:54.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.95,0:08:57.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Rapa Nui!\N--It's Rapa Nui!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.62,0:08:58.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He came back!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.95,0:09:01.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness! Rapa Nui!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.22,0:09:04.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He had me so worried!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.56,0:09:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, how big a pain can one guy be?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.56,0:09:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.56,0:09:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--It can't be...!\N--Professor?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.90,0:09:20.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ape's Concert was maintained in\Na delicate balance to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.24,0:09:23.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you set off a large\Nexplosion in a place like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.24,0:09:26.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there's no telling what might happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.91,0:09:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.25,0:09:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The warping of space is expanding quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.92,0:09:36.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, we'll be caught in it,\Nand all of us will croak!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.25,0:09:38.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.26,0:09:41.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could this happen? Rainbow Tower...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.59,0:09:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...has completely sunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.93,0:09:53.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, as unfinished as it was,\Nit wasn't reinforced enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.27,0:09:55.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But no matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.27,0:10:00.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, my men won't be coming\Nafter me. The treasure is all mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.96,0:10:20.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sky is falling in!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.97,0:10:23.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's not much time. An hour, maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.63,0:10:25.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad! We have to get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.97,0:10:28.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But how?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.97,0:10:32.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The author of this book\Nonce visited Ape's Concert.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.98,0:10:35.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The way out must be written\Nin here somewhere, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.98,0:10:37.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.65,0:10:39.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Continued in the last volume."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.98,0:10:42.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And where is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.32,0:10:44.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.66,0:10:47.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.33,0:10:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.66,0:10:51.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy, that light!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.33,0:10:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the light of the sun...\Nthe light of the setting sun!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.67,0:10:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Setting sun?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.67,0:10:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. The light of the sun is\Nshining in through a crack in space!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.00,0:11:01.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We followed that light, and got outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.94,0:11:02.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.94,0:11:06.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry! That light could disappear at any time!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.61,0:11:10.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unfurl the sails! Everyone,\Nman the oars as hard as you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.62,0:11:12.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you guys come on, too! Give us a hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.95,0:11:14.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're getting out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.29,0:11:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.30,0:11:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what are you doing?! Row right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.30,0:11:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.31,0:11:39.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Ah, they broke!\N--What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.31,0:11:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, not good!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.65,0:11:43.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, this is bad! The light\Nis starting to disappear!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.98,0:11:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, this is the end...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.65,0:11:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys get off and push us from behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.49,0:11:48.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.65,0:11:50.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, if we all flutter kick, then maybe we...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.66,0:11:51.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will not!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.99,0:11:55.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If only we could get a tailwind to blow us...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.99,0:11:58.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just need the wind to blow, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.33,0:12:00.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on! What are you gonna do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.26,0:12:03.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blow up our ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.27,0:12:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was originally a navy ship, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.27,0:12:08.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fully loaded with\Ncannonballs. If we light those,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.61,0:12:10.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it should give you a fairly powerful tailwind.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.61,0:12:11.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.61,0:12:14.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Rapa Nui! If you do that, what...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.95,0:12:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...what will happen to you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.62,0:12:24.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my treasure! Mine! This is\Nwhy I can't give up being mayor!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.63,0:12:37.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, our friends were\Nsupposedly inside that mist.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.64,0:12:42.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened? Don't tell me\Nyou're the only one who came back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.31,0:12:45.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.65,0:12:51.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.66,0:13:00.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rapa Nui!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.93,0:13:03.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, guys! Where are you going?! Come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.26,0:13:05.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are the Pumpkin Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.26,0:13:09.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're friends, who swore we'd\Nstay together until we died!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.27,0:13:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.60,0:13:13.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rapa Nui dove in to save you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.94,0:13:15.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let what he's done be for nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.94,0:13:18.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all trying to get killed together?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.61,0:13:20.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not going to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.95,0:13:24.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Henzo, I promise, we're coming back!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.28,0:13:28.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how many years it takes,\Nwe're coming back to Luluka!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.29,0:13:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isoka...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.29,0:13:34.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't you go thinking that you\Nwon't answer for striking the mayor!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.63,0:13:37.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll have to pay the "hitting the\Nmayor" tax of 90 million Berries!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.63,0:13:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.30,0:13:41.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.63,0:13:45.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just skip out on it, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.64,0:13:48.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Paying taxes is a citizen's duty!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.31,0:13:51.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How is a pirate obligated to pay taxes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.31,0:13:52.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Er, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.98,0:13:54.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.31,0:13:56.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Rainbow Mist is disappearing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.98,0:13:58.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.98,0:14:03.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What will happen to Luffy and everyone else?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.92,0:14:07.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, none of them can come back! Not ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.26,0:14:14.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how hard you guys try,\Nmy power is unshakable!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.95,0:14:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.95,0:14:36.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What?!\N--What the...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.59,0:15:10.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Merry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.25,0:15:12.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are those guys all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.60,0:15:20.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aah! My mansion!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.60,0:15:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of my possessions are being carried away!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.95,0:15:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Guys!\N--Nami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.95,0:15:45.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, how can this happen?!\NMy precious ship...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.62,0:15:47.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Sanji, long time no see!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.29,0:15:49.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.29,0:15:50.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.29,0:15:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, man, am I annoyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.30,0:15:54.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, Nami-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.97,0:15:58.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of the treasure she left\Non deck got blown away.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.64,0:16:01.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Best not to get too close to her right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.91,0:16:05.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's far enough, pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.24,0:16:08.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--The navy!\N--They're the same ones that were chasing us!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.18,0:16:15.85,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Justice"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.58,0:16:13.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help us! These guys are terrible criminals,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.25,0:16:17.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who have taken every last bit\Nof the mayor's property!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.26,0:16:20.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the ring of Princess Illusia,\Na treasure which was stolen
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.26,0:16:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,by pirates a hundred years ago,\Nand has been missing ever since.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.60,0:16:25.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you have this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.93,0:16:27.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.27,0:16:29.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't steal it, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.27,0:16:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, of course not! This was a treasure\Nthat was resting in Ape's Concert!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.94,0:16:37.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes, we just pulled it out of a shipwreck!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.61,0:16:41.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. What you're saying is,\Nit doesn't belong to anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.61,0:16:42.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.61,0:16:45.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Major, we've discovered a large pile of treasure
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.28,0:16:47.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that we believe was carried out of there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.62,0:16:50.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, the navy will be confiscating all of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.62,0:16:53.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it! You're not laying\Na finger on that treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.96,0:16:55.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That treasure is mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.96,0:16:59.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Any treasure without an owner\Nbelongs to the World Government.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.30,0:17:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it has been embezzled, it will\Nbe considered an act of piracy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.90,0:17:05.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine with me! I'm a pirate to begin with!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.57,0:17:07.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever I want, I take by force!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.91,0:17:10.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.24,0:17:12.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will take that as your confession.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.24,0:17:14.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that okay with you, Wetton the pirate?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.91,0:17:16.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.59,0:17:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You couldn't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.86,0:17:33.20,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Justice"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.93,0:17:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rapa Nui...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.60,0:17:32.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.93,0:17:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I promised that we'd come back, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.27,0:17:38.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isoka?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.27,0:17:40.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take all of Wetton's gang into custody.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.61,0:17:42.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.94,0:17:50.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are all alive? B-But how?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.28,0:17:54.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At the moment of the explosion,\Nwe were thrown into the outside world, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.85,0:17:58.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, it was the world 50 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.62,0:18:02.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure enough, that mist warped\Nthe axis of time, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.89,0:18:05.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why didn't you come here sooner?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.56,0:18:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to defeat Wetton, who\Nabused the mantle of his authority,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.90,0:18:14.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought we would need to use another\Nauthority-- the power of the navy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.57,0:18:19.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But in order to gain that high\Na rank, it took me a little time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.24,0:18:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.25,0:18:24.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I may be wearing the uniform\Nof the navy, but in my heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.58,0:18:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still a Pumpkin Pirate,\Nand Henzo, I'm your friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.92,0:18:32.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For now, and forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.26,0:18:36.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rapa Nui...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.93,0:18:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, I forgot to mention this, Luffy Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.60,0:18:47.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but you're under arrest, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.27,0:18:49.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What?!\N--You're heartless!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.61,0:18:53.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you forgotten how you owe\Nme for feeding you, you jerk?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.61,0:18:56.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As a member of the navy,\Ncharged with upholding justice,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.61,0:18:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't just let a pirate who has\Na bounty get away. However...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.95,0:19:03.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can this be?! Right now, we have\Nto escort Wetton and his gang
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.22,0:19:05.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,back to Navy Headquarters! But if we do that,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.89,0:19:09.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Luffy Pirates are going to\Nend up slipping away from us!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.89,0:19:12.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But they're just too much for us to handle!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.56,0:19:14.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Request assistance from\Nthe naval base at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.57,0:19:17.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it won't be until tomorrow or\Nthe next day that they'll arrive!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.24,0:19:21.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they escape during that time,\Nthat's the end of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.77,0:19:23.01,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Justice"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.24,0:19:24.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aah, I give up! I can't do anything about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.91,0:19:27.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That sure sounded like a put-on.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.58,0:19:34.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't do any full-fledged repairs right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.25,0:19:39.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those emergency measures should\Nat least keep the water out, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.92,0:19:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Luffy, and all of your friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.60,0:19:47.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, the research that I carried\Non all these years is at an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.93,0:19:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't have that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.93,0:19:53.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no telling when the Rainbow\NMist is going to appear, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.27,0:19:56.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With that thing out there,\Nwe can't go out to sea in peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.94,0:19:58.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We want you to make us some gear,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.94,0:20:01.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to help us avoid the Rainbow Mist.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.95,0:20:05.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That will be an easy task.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.96,0:20:16.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Rainbow Mist is a land of eternity.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.63,0:20:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It has neither daytime, nor nighttime.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.96,0:20:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One never gets sick, or grows old.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.30,0:20:30.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sea shines emerald, and the sky\Nenvelops us deeply, like milk.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.64,0:20:33.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The countless ships that\Nbecome captives of this land
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.31,0:20:36.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,had immeasurable treasures\Nresting within them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.65,0:20:42.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was indeed the last\Nparadise remaining on earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.65,0:20:45.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were the kings of that land of eternity.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.99,0:20:47.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We routed the pirates that came invading,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.99,0:20:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and kept the peace in paradise.\NOur name was the Pumpkin Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.00,0:20:56.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would like to write down\Nthe many unusual adventures
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.33,0:21:01.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we went through inside the mist...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.27,0:21:06.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...for the sake of the adventurers\Nwho will visit this land hereafter.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.28,0:21:14.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The name of the adventurers belongs to those
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.95,0:21:19.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,whose debt we are in for\Nleading us back out into the world--
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.29,0:21:21.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Luffy Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.96,0:21:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, that sure was an interesting place.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.63,0:21:29.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? I've had enough of that ship graveyard!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.97,0:21:32.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's not like I wanna live there,\Nbut I wanna visit from time to time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.97,0:21:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was it really that nice?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.97,0:21:37.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hm? Rain?\N--It's... not rain...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.64,0:21:39.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hail?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.98,0:21:43.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... something's fall--
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.49,0:22:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, beyond the never-ending sky
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.60,0:22:13.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The future that I once saw\Nis now starting to take shape
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.95,0:22:28.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are days where I almost lose to myself
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.46,0:22:36.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When that happened, there was\Nsomeplace warm I could go
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.83,0:22:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The friends I took pride in\Nalways, without fail,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.97,0:22:53.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,pushed me onwards, didn't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.99,0:23:02.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, the stars are pouring\Ndown underneath the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.26,0:23:04.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This unique moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.60,0:23:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.60,0:23:16.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our Log Pose is broken!\NIt's stuck pointing upwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.27,0:23:17.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What?!\N--That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.88,0:23:20.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was updated by an island\Nwith stronger magnetism.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.61,0:23:23.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--If it's pointing up, it's a sky island.\N--Sky island?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.61,0:23:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, that ship fell from there?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.28,0:23:27.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.62,0:23:30.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Caught Log! The King of Salvagers, Masira!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.62,0:23:32.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.96,0:23:37.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
